Smart sync only runs when the logged-in user has both of these permissions (or is super admin):

access_daftartransaksi – access to Daftar Transaksi
access_kasir_bayar_button – access to the Bayar button (pay)
Summary:

Super admin → smart sync always allowed (no permission check).
Other users → smart sync allowed only if they have both:
access_daftartransaksi
access_kasir_bayar_button
No user / logged out → smart sync off.
User with only one of the two → smart sync off.